游戏获得媒体称赞，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上汇总得分为91%<ref name="metacritic" />，日本杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》为游戏打出36/40<ref name="fami" />。评论集中称赞游戏的图形和游戏性，并批评重复的单人模式。《马里奥赛车DS》获得[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]和[[IGN|IGN]]的编辑推荐奖<ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="ign" />。游戏获得GameSpot的最佳多人游戏<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=2&page=17 |title=Best Multiplayer Game |publisher=GameSpot |archive-date=2006-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061020182908/http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=2&page=17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、最佳驾驶游戏和最佳DS游戏提名<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=4&page=6 |title=Best Driving Game |publisher=GameSpot |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105083747/http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=4&page=6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并摘取最后一项奖项<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=5&page=2 |title=Best DS Game |publisher=GameSpot |archive-date=2007-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930220941/http://www.gamespot.com/pages/features/bestof2005/index.php?day=5&page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏获得《[[G-Phoria|G-Phoria]]》的最佳掌机游戏奖<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/ds/driving/mariokartds/news.html?sid=6155587 |title=G4 announces G-phoria winners, books Jack Thompson |publisher=GameSpot |date=2006-08-10 |author=Thorsen, Tor |archive-date=2016-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811102410/http://www.gamespot.com/mario-kart-ds/news/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。IGN授予游戏2005年度最佳竞速/驾驶游戏奖<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2005/ds/21.html |title=Game of the Year |publisher=IGN |archive-date=2008-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081014191253/http://bestof.ign.com/2005/ds/21.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

几家评论称赞游戏没有辜负前作创下的标准。[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]认为，虽然游戏在线部分恼人，但单人模式和本地无线模式远补偿了此项<ref name="gamespy" />。任天堂世界报道称“以往马里奥赛车游戏的最佳功能又回来了”，并和《马里奥赛车DS》的新功能配合，铸成了“有史以来印象最深刻的任天堂DS游戏，也是马里奥赛车系列的最佳游戏”<ref name="nwr">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/reviewArt.cfm?CFID=92669d9c-07c5-49b6-9881-f1dba26b49f3&CFTOKEN=0&artid=4450 |title=Mario Kart DS |publisher=Nintendo World Report |date=2005-11-19 |author=Sklens, Mike |archive-date=2010-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201050602/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/reviewArt.cfm?artid=4450 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。持同样观点的《[[X-Play|X-Play]]》表示，游戏突破一切期待，成为“全版本——掌机还是其它——卡丁车竞速游戏里最棒的”<ref name="xplay">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/211/Mario_Kart_DS.html |title=Mario Kart DS |work=X-Play |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827083313/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/211/Mario_Kart_DS.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[GameZone|GameZone]]确信《马里奥赛车DS》用创造性的赛道和“出色的”多人模式和比其他同类型道具类竞速游戏更高的重复可玩性的价值“没有令这个系列失望”<ref name="gamezone">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-09 |url=http://nds.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r24080.htm |title=Mario Kart DS Review |publisher=GameZone |date=2005-12-12 |author=Bedigian, Louis |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227070106/http://nds.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r24080.htm |archivedate=2008-12-27 }} </ref>。[[CBS新闻|CBS新闻]]的亚历杭德罗·K·布朗称赞游戏以独特方法使用了任天堂DS特性，如麦克风和无线连接<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-02-03 |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2005/11/18/tech/gamecore/main1058578.shtml |title=Mario Kart DS Dominates |publisher=CBS News |date=2005-11-18 |author=Vitka, William |archive-date=2013-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511161130/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2005/11/18/tech/gamecore/main1058578.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的一篇文章中，《马里奥赛车DS》击败《[[口袋妖怪_黑·白|口袋妖怪 黑·白]]》（第二名）和《[[侠盗猎车手：血战唐人街|侠盗猎车手：血战唐人街]]》（第三名），成为史上最佳任天堂DS游戏<ref>{{cite web | accessdate=2013-02-03 | url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-ds-games/ | title=Best DS Games | publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] | author=GamesRadar staff | date=2012-09-15 | archive-date=2012-06-09 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68I36y7QO?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-ds-games/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

IGN称赞《马里奥赛车DS》的游戏性和设计深度，并称难以想象任天堂如何做出胜过本作的马里奥赛车游戏<ref name="ign" />。GameSpot称游戏是马里奥赛车系列的“显著进步”，部分原因是系列首次采用联机游戏<ref name="gamespot" />。[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]称游戏用单人和多人模式“完成职责”<ref name="gamerev">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/ds/mario_kart_ds |title=Mario Kart DS - DS Review |publisher=Game Revolution |date=2005-11-15 |author=Silverman, Ben |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080512161108/http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/ds/mario_kart_ds |archivedate=2008-05-12 }}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]称游戏“出奇抓人的包装”是“和史上所有主机作品比肩的携带式竞速游戏”<ref name="1up" />。电子游戏杂志《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》对游戏多样的赛手、赛道和模式以及多人选项表示称赞，称本作是任天堂爱好者的“必玩游戏”及任天堂DS机主的必备游戏<ref name="gamepro">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/49814/mario-kart-ds/ |title=Mario Kart DS |work=GamePro |date=2005-11-14 |author=Burner, Rice |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914153322/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/49814/mario-kart-ds/ |archivedate=2008-09-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]》称《马里奥赛车DS》虽有少量图形有瑕疵，却是“最齐全”的马里奥赛车游戏<ref name="cvg">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=130044 |title=Mario Kart DS |work=Computer and Video Games |date=2005-11-24 |archive-date=2018-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926205449/https://www.gamesradar.com/?id=130044 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]对游戏多人模式表示满意，称游戏“真正实现于他人同乐”<ref name="eurogamer" />。中国大陆杂志《[[游戏机实用技术|游戏机实用技术]]》观点相同，但称游戏机十字键较浅阻碍了部分技巧的使用<ref name="UCG" />。英国出版物《[[GamesTM|GamesTM]]》批评游戏“除马里奥赛车概念文饰外无他”<ref name="gamestm">{{cite journal |title=Mario Kart DS review |journal=GamesTM | date = 2006-05 |page=99 }}</ref>，电子游戏网站Nintendophiles对“单调的”多人模式和“简单的电脑玩家”表示失望<ref name="nintendophiles">{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.n-philes.com/reviews/165/mario-kart-ds/ |title=Mario Kart DS (DSN) |publisher=Nintendophiles |date=2005-11-28 |author=Biersdorf, Dan |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080620230039/http://www.n-philes.com/reviews/165/mario-kart-ds/ |archivedate=2008-06-20 }}</ref>。

游戏是首款任天堂DS游戏机任天堂Wi-Fi连接功能的作品。美国有11.2万玩家在首周购买游戏，其中5.2万使用任天堂Wi-Fi连接和他人联网对战<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2009-01-08 |url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/11_22_05_07_04AM.htm |title=Nearly Half of Mario Kart DS Owners Play Via Wi-Fi in First Week |publisher=GameZone |date=2005-11-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090218192602/http://www.gamezone.com/news/11_22_05_07_04AM.htm |archivedate=2009-02-18 }} </ref>。《马里奥赛车DS》发售首月成为美国月度最畅销掌机游戏<ref>{{cite journal |title=Best Selling Games |journal=NPD | date = 2005-12 }}</ref>。游戏成为2008年第10畅销游戏暨最畅销任天堂DS游戏<ref>{{cite web |title=NPD: Nintendo Drives '08 Industry Sales Past $21 Billion |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |publisher=GameDaily |accessdate=2009-01-15 |date=2009-01-15 |archive-date=2009-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117013042/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在日本首周售出22.4万<ref>{{cite journal |title=Best Selling Games |journal=Famitsu | date = 2006-01 }}</ref>。《马里奥赛车DS》到2008年7月时售出311.2万<ref>{{cite journal |title=Best Selling Games |journal=Famitsu | date = 2008-07 }}</ref>，2009年1月时售出322.5万，成为主机发售当时第6畅销游戏<ref>{{cite journal |title=Best Selling Games |journal=Famitsu | date = 2009-01 }}</ref>。游戏在2013年时是第三畅销任天堂DS游戏<ref name="mar13">{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/software/ds.html|title=Top Selling Software Sales Units - Nintendo DS Software|publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date=2013-03-31|accessdate=2013-04-24|archive-date=2016-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427092514/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/software/ds.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2014年6月时全球销量2356万<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2014/06/02/mario-kart-8-speeds-to-over-1-2-million-sales-in-opening-weekend.aspx|title=Mario Kart 8 Speeds To Over 1.2 Million Sales In Opening Weekend|last=Futter|first=Mike|date=2014-06-02|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|publisher=[[GameStop|GameStop]]|accessdate=2014-06-02|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520144821/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2014/06/02/mario-kart-8-speeds-to-over-1-2-million-sales-in-opening-weekend.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{clear}}

